- Subtrees â‰ˆ isolated system components  
- Splitting â‰ˆ segmentation or trust boundaries  
- Evaluating all splits â‰ˆ attack surface analysis  

In security, you donâ€™t just protect the whole system â€” you evaluate the impact of isolating every component.

